data.description: SELLER TO PAY $10,000 TOWARDS A 2/1 rate buy down OR ALL CLOSING COSTS ++++ A 2/1 RATE BUY DOWN MEANS YOUR INTEREST RATE IS 2% LOWER THE FIRST YEAR AND 1% LOWER THE 2nd YEAR, THEN YOU HAVE THE OPTION DO REFINANCE+++  Welcome to 804 Sienna Way nestled in the charming town of Summerville, South Carolina.  This home is a true gem waiting for you to call it home. This meticulously maintained residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a wealth of desirable features, this property is sure to capture your heart.As you enter, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area, adorned with abundant natural light that accentuates the open layout.The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting modern appliances, ample counter space, and a cozy breakfast nook where you can savor your morning coffee.  All four bedrooms are thoughtfully designed and located upstairs, ensuring a peaceful retreat for the whole family. The owner's suite is a haven of relaxation, featuring generous closet space and an en-suite bathroom that pampers with its spa-like amenities.  Step outside to the private backyard oasis, perfect for entertaining, gardening, or simply unwinding in the fresh South Carolina air. Imagine hosting weekend barbecues on the patio or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars.  804 Sienna has some unseen amazing features as well!  The whole house is wired for fiber internet and surround sound and Hometeam Pest Defense has tubes throughout the home to spray for bugs- called Taexx treatment- very handy in the Lowcountry.    Located in a thriving community, 804 Sienna Way offers easy access to local schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Summerville's historic charm and vibrant atmosphere are just moments away, providing endless opportunities for recreation and entertainment.  Don't miss your chance to make this house your forever home. 804 Sienna Way is more than just a property; it's a place where cherished memories are made. Schedule your showing today and discover the lifestyle you've been dreaming of in Summerville, SC.
